    "causal_summary": "Two classifiers route every non-trivial task: `gate-3-classifier.ts` is a HARD-block gate for file-modification intent detection, and `skill_advisor.py` mandates skill invocation at confidence ≥ 0.8. Neither has had an offline accuracy evaluation. CLAUDE.md admits specific false-positive tokens (`analyze`, `decompose`, `phase`) on Gate 3, but the residual error surface of both classifiers is unquantified.",
